# Personal Portfolio Website

Welcome to the GitHub repository for my personal portfolio website! This project showcases my work, skills, and projects through a dynamic and interactive interface built using modern web development technologies.

You can visit the live version of the website here: [jear-bear.github.io](https://jear-bear.github.io).

